## Game Loops

Almost every video game you've ever played runs inside a massive `while` loop!

```swift
var isGameOver = false

while isGameOver == false {
   // 1. Check for player input
   // 2. Update character positions
   // 3. Draw the screen
}
```
The game keeps running 60 times a second until the player loses, making `isGameOver` true.
